org.apache.flex.compiler.internal.scopes

Class SmallDefinitionStore4

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flex.compiler.internal.scopes.SmallDefinitionStoreBase
      • org.apache.flex.compiler.internal.scopes.SmallDefinitionStore4
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IDefinitionStore

    public final class SmallDefinitionStore4
extends SmallDefinitionStoreBase
    An implementation of IDefinitionStore for storing up to 4 definitions using 4 fields rather than a map. Many scopes contain only a few definitions.

    The methods of this class are optimized to use unrolled loops.

      • createLargerStore

        public IDefinitionStore createLargerStore()
        Description copied from interface: IDefinitionStore
        Creates another definition store with a greater capacity.

        When a call to IDefinitionStore.add(org.apache.flex.compiler.definitions.IDefinition)() on this store returns false (because the store has reached its capacity), call this method to create a larger store and then call add()) on it. The second add() is guaranteed to succeed.

        Returns:
        An IDefinitionStore with a greater capacity.

      • getDefinitionSetByName

        public IDefinitionSet getDefinitionSetByName(String baseName)
        Description copied from interface: IDefinitionStore
        Gets the set of definitions in this store that have a specified base name.

        This method is called very frequently as part of name resolution. All implementations should be fast and avoid creating temporary objects.

      • putDefinitionSetByName

        public void putDefinitionSetByName(String baseName,
                          IDefinitionSet set)
        Description copied from interface: IDefinitionStore
        Puts a specified set of definitions with a specified base name into this store.

        This is only used when a project scope has to replace a definition set in its store because it has converted definition promises in the set to actual definitions.

        Parameters:
        baseName - The base name of the definitions in the set.
        set - The IDefinitionSet of definitions to put into the store.
